-No, you stop.<br>-No, you stop.
<SYNC Start=624222><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=625191><P Class=ENCC>
Why don't I sit here<br>and then you'll both stop it?
<SYNC Start=627751><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=631197><P Class=ENCC>
Okay. So, what do you want to do?
<SYNC Start=633097><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=633799><P Class=ENCC>
Let's do something crazy.
<SYNC Start=635699><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=635901><P Class=ENCC>
I know, let's rest and drink<br>lots of fluids.
<SYNC Start=638927><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=640072><P Class=ENCC>
Okay, I'll rest.
<SYNC Start=641437><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=641641><P Class=ENCC>
But if I'm going to bed,<br>then you're coming with me.
<SYNC Start=646203><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=647913><P Class=ENCC>
