<SYNC Start=651644><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=651917><P Class=ENCC>
drippy here.
<SYNC Start=653282><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=655254><P Class=ENCC>
Are you saying that you don't<br>want to get with this?
<SYNC Start=659623><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=664130><P Class=ENCC>
