<SYNC Start=685951><P Class=ENCC>
Let me prove it to you.
<SYNC Start=687942><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=688954><P Class=ENCC>
We are two healthy people<br>in the prime of lime.
<SYNC Start=693948><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=694827><P Class=ENCC>
See, that's the thing, I would like<br>to stay in the "prime of lime."
<SYNC Start=699287><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=705805><P Class=ENCC>
Oh, okay, now I'll do it.
<SYNC Start=708273><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=711944><P Class=ENCC>
