<SYNC Start=742835><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=743509><P Class=ENCC>
With Ross and my sister?
<SYNC Start=745374><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=748380><P Class=ENCC>
With my sister Jill<br>and my ex-boyfriend Ross?
<SYNC Start=751577><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
