-Oh, there is no way.<br>-Okay, then.
<SYNC Start=755787><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=755988><P Class=ENCC>
Oh, my God! I cannot believe that!
<SYNC Start=758923><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=759558><P Class=ENCC>
I don't like it when he dates anyone,<br>but my sister?
<SYNC Start=762527><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=762728><P Class=ENCC>
Isn't that incest or something?
<SYNC Start=764753><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=765898><P Class=ENCC>
And they're gonna have sex.
<SYNC Start=767866><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=768434><P Class=ENCC>
