<SYNC Start=771335><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=771537><P Class=ENCC>
This is just terrible.<br>This is just terrible.
<SYNC Start=774062><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=774273><P Class=ENCC>
And I can't stop it.<br>I don't own Ross.
<SYNC Start=776673><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=776876><P Class=ENCC>
And Jill should be able to do<br>what she wants to do.
<SYNC Start=779845><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=780079><P Class=ENCC>
Oh, my God, I can't believe Ross<br>is marrying my little sister.
<SYNC Start=784015><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=784250><P Class=ENCC>
This is the worst thing that<br>could've ever happened to me.
<SYNC Start=787515><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=789221><P Class=ENCC>
But great news about<br>the apartment pants, huh?
<SYNC Start=792122><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=794527><P Class=ENCC>
That'll be $3.85.
<SYNC Start=796085><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=796362><P Class=ENCC>
What? Yesterday you said<br>I was too pretty to pay.
<SYNC Start=799229><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=799732><P Class=ENCC>
It's just, I can't,<br>because my manager said that I..
<SYNC Start=802963><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=804570><P Class=ENCC>
Happy birthday to you
<SYNC Start=807767><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=807973><P Class=ENCC>
Happy birthday to you
<SYNC Start=810271><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=810476><P Class=ENCC>
-Happy birthday, dear Annie..<br>-Amy!
<SYNC Start=813411><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
