<SYNC Start=838561><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=838804><P Class=ENCC>
How strong am I?
<SYNC Start=839998><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=841607><P Class=ENCC>
That is great.
<SYNC Start=842938><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=843242><P Class=ENCC>
You know who doesn't have to<br>job-hunt? Ross.
<SYNC Start=846575><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
