<SYNC Start=849178><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=849515><P Class=ENCC>
So you guys talked? So you get along?<br>So you're gonna go out?
<SYNC Start=853246><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=855187><P Class=ENCC>
Me go out with Ross? No.
<SYNC Start=857849><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=858090><P Class=ENCC>
God, no.<br>What would make you think that?
<SYNC Start=860524><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=861160><P Class=ENCC>
Phoebe...
<SYNC Start=862252><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=862494><P Class=ENCC>
said she thought she saw something<br>between you guys.
<SYNC Start=865759><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=865998><P Class=ENCC>
I mean, he's nice.
<SYNC Start=867761><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=868000><P Class=ENCC>
He's the kind you're friends with,<br>but not the kind you date.
<SYNC Start=871458><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=871670><P Class=ENCC>
