<SYNC Start=876041><P Class=ENCC>
Not so much.
<SYNC Start=877440><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=878978><P Class=ENCC>
Oh, not so much. What do you mean?<br>Is there something wrong with Ross?
<SYNC Start=883881><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=884183><P Class=ENCC>
No, no, no. He's just...
<SYNC Start=885844><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=886118><P Class=ENCC>
