<SYNC Start=891847><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=892124><P Class=ENCC>
You think so too?
<SYNC Start=893682><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=894693><P Class=ENCC>
No. Ross is not a geek.
<SYNC Start=897025><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=897897><P Class=ENCC>
Then let's just say<br>he's not my type.
<SYNC Start=900127><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=900332><P Class=ENCC>
Handsome is not your type?
<SYNC Start=902857><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
