Smart, kind, good kisser.
<SYNC Start=904830><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=905037><P Class=ENCC>
What, those things aren't<br>on your list?
<SYNC Start=907232><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=907473><P Class=ENCC>
Ross is great.<br>You'd be lucky to be with him.
<SYNC Start=910169><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=910676><P Class=ENCC>
If it means that much,<br>then I'll ask him out.
<SYNC Start=913236><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=913512><P Class=ENCC>
Oh, no. That's not what I meant.
<SYNC Start=916037><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=916315><P Class=ENCC>
You know what? You're right.
<SYNC Start=918010><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=918250><P Class=ENCC>
