<SYNC Start=920548><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=921220><P Class=ENCC>
Yeah, but he's not your type.
<SYNC Start=923211><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=924023><P Class=ENCC>
But maybe that's good.
<SYNC Start=925388><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=925591><P Class=ENCC>
I'm doing all these different things.
<SYNC Start=927684><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=927927><P Class=ENCC>
