<SYNC Start=1052951><P Class=ENCC>
Damn it!
<SYNC Start=1054418><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1059691><P Class=ENCC>
Did you tell your sister<br>to ask me out?
<SYNC Start=1061989><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1063028><P Class=ENCC>
-Well, yeah.<br>-Oh, wow! I mean, wow.
<SYNC Start=1066862><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1068434><P Class=ENCC>
I think she's cute, but...
<SYNC Start=1071130><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1071370><P Class=ENCC>
