<SYNC Start=1086842><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1087119><P Class=ENCC>
I mean, after all we've been through.
<SYNC Start=1089713><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1090155><P Class=ENCC>
