<SYNC Start=1189755><P Class=ENCC>
What about never sleeping<br>with sick people?
<SYNC Start=1192053><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1192424><P Class=ENCC>
Well, that was before<br>all the vaporizing action.
<SYNC Start=1196417><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1198730><P Class=ENCC>
Okay, if you really<br>want to have sex.
<SYNC Start=1200721><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
