Worked like a charm.
<SYNC Start=1205169><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1211677><P Class=ENCC>
Why are you here?
<SYNC Start=1212666><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1213178><P Class=ENCC>
